We provide a helper method which aims to make plotting indicators simple. For further information on the charting API please see our Charting section.

private SharpeRatio _sr;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_sr = SR(symbol, sharpePeriod);

// In OnData()
if (_sr.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "SR Current", _sr.Current);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.sr = self.SR(symbol, sharpePeriod)

# In OnData()
if self.sr.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "SR Current", self.sr.Current)
